39:21.779 --> 39:24.475
You tried to have me killed.

39:24.549 --> 39:26.642
- Nothing personal.
- [ Chuckles ]

39:26.717 --> 39:30.448
Do the same in myposition. Michael,
you keep thinking that this is about me.

39:30.521 --> 39:35.823
Banish that thought. You're on the edge of
