39:39.530 --> 39:43.159
Powerful, dangerous people.
And, man, are they upset with me.

39:43.234 --> 39:47.170
I misread you, Michael.
Didn't expectyou to buck quite so much.

39:47.238 --> 39:48.762
- You're making everyone nervous.
- [ Gunshot]

39:48.839 --> 39:50.602
[ Grunts ]

39:59.250 --> 40:01.844
[Sirens Wailing]

