40:59.410 --> 41:02.573
- Somebody called them before the shot was fired.
- [ Sighs ]

41:02.647 --> 41:04.581
This is deep, Bro.

41:08.486 --> 41:10.511
Nate, I wantyou
to go pick up Mom.

41:10.588 --> 41:13.182
It's about timeyou two
got out oftown.

41:13.257 --> 41:15.589
Right.

