Hurry up.
I got 'em pinned down.

44:50.333 --> 44:52.392
[ Truck Engine Starts ]

45:01.177 --> 45:05.477
[ Michael Narrating] A good trap
doesn't scare people-- it makes them curious.

45:10.987 --> 45:13.148
A speeding truck
makes people scatter.

45:13.223 --> 45:16.090
A slow-moving truck,
on the other hand...

45:16.159 --> 45:18.719
makes people want
to take a closer look.

45:24.334 --> 45:26.564
- T ake cover! Go! Go!
- [ Clamoring ]

45:46.856 --> 45:50.292
That was i nsane.
