45:50.360 --> 45:53.124
Sam had a job.
Things didn't go as planned.

45:53.196 --> 45:56.996
- [ Nate ] You're out ofyour mind!
- What happened with Cowan?

45:57.066 --> 46:00.399
Yeah. Things didn't go
as planned with that either.

46:03.306 --> 46:05.831
He's dead, Fi.
They shot him whilewewere talking.

46:05.908 --> 46:08.172
- Did you get anything?
- A little.

46:08.244 --> 46:11.179
He said the people heworks for--
they have plans for me.

46:11.247 --> 46:14.375
Yeah, well, that's intriguing.
What the hell does it mean?

46:14.450 --> 46:16.645
Without knowing who they are,
hard to say.

46:16.719 --> 46:19.847
They might want information.
They might have a job theywant me to do.

46:19.922 --> 46:21.913
I mean,
they shot him for a reason.

46:23.793 --> 46:27.024
Better be a good reason.

46:30.533 --> 46:32.831
- This is your place?
- Yeah.

46:32.902 --> 46:37.100
Well, it's a foreclosure. You know,
I guess they ran out of money in the remodel.

46:37.173 --> 46:39.801
Usually, I can hang out
about three months in a place like this.

46:39.876 --> 46:41.810
You--You know,
you blew up my truck.

46:41.878 --> 46:44.346
- Anyone knowyou're here?
- No, no.

46:44.414 --> 46:46.644
I got a couple clients
in mygolfclub business.

46:46.716 --> 46:50.243
Theyweren't real happywith the way
