Who doyou work for?

47:33.930 --> 47:36.023
[ Chuckling ]
Me?

47:36.099 --> 47:38.033
I don't work for anyone.

47:38.101 --> 47:41.935
I go out there sometimes
just to-- to think.

47:42.004 --> 47:45.064
Take pictures ofthe birds
and the local fauna. You know.

47:45.141 --> 47:48.042
[ Groaning ]

47:48.111 --> 47:51.478
Ooh! Ooh!
You're gettin' good at that.

47:51.547 --> 47:54.448
The guy that came for the woman--
he knew what he was doin'.

47:54.517 --> 47:57.953
- Maybe D.E.A.?
- D.E.A. comes with a team.

47:58.020 --> 48:01.456
D.E.A. brings cops.
