48:01.524 --> 48:04.357
You know, buddy, if I were you,
I'd watch it with the stupid comments.

48:04.427 --> 48:07.760
'Cause, you know, your boss just killed
a lot ofhis own guys outside--

48:11.334 --> 48:14.462
- [ Sighs ]
- Let me guess.

48:14.537 --> 48:17.165
- You're trying to buy time foryour team. Is that it?
- Team?

48:17.240 --> 48:20.801
Uh--Well, there's--
there's no team around here.

48:20.877 --> 48:24.643
- I work alone in a cubicle.
- You work alone? Mm-hmm.

48:24.714 --> 48:26.944
Pretty talkative for a loner.

48:27.016 --> 48:29.678
Called this number three times
when you were at the docks.

48:29.752 --> 48:32.619
- Let me guess. Thatyour boss?
- Nah, that's my boyfriend.

48:32.688 --> 48:35.248
Okay, okay!

48:35.324 --> 48:38.088
[ Sighs ]
Look, I'm D.E.A.

48:38.161 --> 48:41.324
We've been watching you guys for months.
We got a grand jury ready to go.

48:41.998 --> 48:46.492
[ Grunting, Groaning ]

48:46.569 --> 48:49.732
I'm C.I.A.
That's right. C.I.A.

48:49.806 --> 48:52.832
We've been tracking
yourTurkish heroin connection for terrorists.

48:52.909 --> 48:55.503
