48:55.578 --> 48:58.206
Okay.

48:58.281 --> 49:00.511
F.B.I.

49:00.583 --> 49:02.949
We got an informant.

49:03.019 --> 49:05.647
Your guy there--
he works for us.

49:05.721 --> 49:07.985
Isn't that right, Frank?
Come on, tell him.

49:08.057 --> 49:11.356
No use lying now.
He's got us. Come on, Frank!

49:12.962 --> 49:15.658
You're a funny guy.

49:15.731 --> 49:17.665
You're trained, aren'tyou?
Hmm?

49:17.733 --> 49:20.133
Let me guess.

49:20.203 --> 49:22.637
Special Forces?

49:22.705 --> 49:24.866
See, me--
I'm an ex-Green Beret.

49:24.941 --> 49:28.399
Admit nothing,
denyeverything...

49:28.478 --> 49:31.641
make counteraccusations.

49:31.714 --> 49:34.740
Special Forces?
No, no.

49:34.817 --> 49:36.808
I was a Boy Scout
for a while.

49:36.886 --> 49:38.877
Hey, take these
restraints off me.

49:38.955 --> 49:41.048
I'll show you
how to tie a slipknot.

49:41.123 --> 49:42.920
- Let's just kill him.
- And then what?

49:42.992 --> 49:48.487
The girl saw us. We gotta take care
ofthe whole team, plus Gillian.

49:48.564 --> 49:51.829
By the way, seems like
she packed up and left early.

49:51.901 --> 49:55.200
We went by her house.
Must have been in a hurry.

49:55.271 --> 49:57.671
But don't worry.
I'll find her.

49:57.740 --> 50:00.607
I'm really good at that.

50:03.379 --> 50:06.212
- [ Yawning ] Excuse me. I'm sorry.
- [ Chuckling ]

50:06.282 --> 50:09.342
You know what?

50:09.418 --> 50:11.648
Show him what Green Berets
are all about.

50:21.330 --> 50:23.264
[ Grunts ]

50:24.634 --> 50:26.693
There's more...

50:26.769 --> 50:28.930
stashed under
a Fort Lauderdale overpass.

50:29.005 --> 50:30.700
[Michael Narrating]
F.oranyoperative...

50:30.773 --> 50:33.401
stashing weapons
is second nature after a while.

50:33.476 --> 50:35.603
Spies hide guns
like squirrels hide acorns.

50:35.678 --> 50:38.146
You never know when
you'll need some firepower...

50:38.214 --> 50:39.943
or where you'll be
when you need it.

50:40.016 --> 50:42.917
I f we need more than this,
we're doing something very wrong.

50:42.985 --> 50:45.647
Or something very right.

50:45.721 --> 50:48.554
[ Cell Phone Ringing]

50:48.624 --> 50:52.651
- Hello?
- I've got someone here who says he knows you.

50:52.728 --> 50:55.094
Sam?

50:55.164 --> 50:57.098
Yeah, he works for me.

50:57.166 --> 51:00.294
Oh, yeah?
And what kind ofwork do you do?

51:00.369 --> 51:04.601
[ Michael Narrating] Choosing a coverl.D.
on the flyis always a challenge.

51:04.674 --> 51:07.837
- My work?
- Yeah, your work.

51:07.910 --> 51:10.640
What was your man doing
down at the docks taking pictures, huh?

51:10.713 --> 51:12.647
[ Michael Narrating]
When there's no time to think...

51:12.715 --> 51:16.014
it's best to go with something simple
that keeps your options open.

51:16.085 --> 51:18.610
I 'm in the same business you're in.
We're interested in your operation.

51:18.688 --> 51:21.486
- I sent Sam down to do some research.
- Oh, yeah?

51:21.557 --> 51:25.584
- That's not what Sam says.
- I don't train my employees
to talk about my business.

51:25.661 --> 51:28.255
Listen to me, not to him.
Who am I talking to?

51:28.331 --> 51:31.129
Hmm. I thinkyou know
enough about me for now.

51:31.200 --> 51:33.134
Let me askyou a question.
You thought what?

51:33.202 --> 51:35.136
You could just come down here
and rip me off?

51:35.204 --> 51:37.138
I'm just checking out
the competition.

51:37.206 --> 51:39.936
You know, move to a new market,
check out the lay ofthe land.

51:40.009 --> 51:43.376
Point is, the man you have
is a valued employee.

51:43.446 --> 51:46.006
I want him back.
I'm willing to deal.

51:46.082 --> 51:49.051
Let's set a meet.
We'll figure out a price.

51:49.118 --> 51:52.713
I'm happyto negotiate,
but I do not pay for damaged merchandise.

51:52.788 --> 51:56.155
- I want proof oflife.
- You got e-mail?

51:56.225 --> 51:57.817
[ Mouthing Word ]

51:59.095 --> 52:03.589
Wake up, Sammyboy.
Picture time.

52:07.770 --> 52:10.261
[ Groans ]
So, uh...

52:10.339 --> 52:12.273
probably gonna be
my last photo, right?

52:12.341 --> 52:14.275
I mean, you got these plans
to kill everybody.

52:14.343 --> 52:18.973
So I'm thinkin',
I should look good for this, huh?

52:19.048 --> 52:21.949
Let's see.

52:22.018 --> 52:24.543
Nice. I'll send it toyour mama.

52:38.000 --> 52:40.833
[Michael Narrating]
F.reon is available at most computerstores.

52:40.903 --> 52:45.772
Buya can ofscreen duster, turn it upside down,
